Description: The total cumulative hit time in the AOI (AOI_NAME), per epoch.
The time from the start of the epoch to the first hit in the AOI (AOI_NAME), per epoch. Is zero if the epoch started during a hit, blank/NaN if the epoch did not feature any hits.
The duration of the first hit in the AOI (AOI_NAME), per epoch. If the epoch started or ended while a hit was active, only the duration during the epoch is considered.
The total distinct times that the AOI (AOI_NAME) was hit, per epoch.
